Field Label: ## Eating Disorders
### General Probes\r\n\r\nEarlier you told me some things about your eating habits and your weight. Now I would like to ask you some questions about that.

### Bulimia

Now I am going to ask you about eating binges.  An eating binge is when someone stuffs themselves with a whole lot of food in a short time - like several whole pizzas or a whole chocolate cake or several containers of ice cream - and they don't seem to be able to control how much they eat. 

 Have you ever had an eating binge like that?
During these binges were you afraid you could not stop eating, or that your eating was out of control?
On average, how often per week or month did you have eating binges?  \r\n\r\n _(N times per week, month)_
How long did this period of over-eating last? \r\n\r\n _(N days, N weeks, N months)_

### Episodes: Onset

How old were you the **first time** you did these (list behaviors)? 

 _Code 998 if "always", 999 if "unknown"._
### Episodes: Offset\r\n\r\nDo you currently have times when you do these behaviors?
How old were you the **last time** you did this behavior? \r\n\r\n _Code 998 if "always", 999 if "unknown"._

### Compensatory Behavior

Did you do anything to make yourself thin, like: 

 Making yourself throw up?
Taking diet pills or any other pills/medicine to help you lose weight?
Which substances?
Going on a very strict diet (eating very few calories)?
Fasting (not eating at all)?
Exercising a lot?
Chewing and spitting out food rather than swallowing?
Other
Specify (Other):
How old were you the **first time** you did any of these behaviors (list)?  \r\n\r\n _Code 998 if "always", 999 if "unknown"._

Field Label: ### Body Image\r\n\r\nDuring this time (did you ever have a time when you) were you a lot more concerned about your weight and/or shape than most people your age?
### Anorexia Nervosa\r\n\r\nWas there ever a time when you weighed much less than other people thought you ought to weigh?  Has anyone ever worried that you were much too thin?
### Weight Loss\r\n\r\nAt that time, had you lost a lot of weight on purpose?
In the past, did you keep your weight down on purpose?
What was your lowest weight at that time?
About how tall were you at that time? \r\n\r\n _(Record feet and inches in this format: 5' 10)_
How old were you at the time?   \r\n\r\n _Code 998 if "always", 999 if "unknown"._
_INTERVIEWER: Is participant's lowest weight 85% or lower than normal?  See Participant Card (Height/Weight)_
### Anorexia Binging Type/Bulimia Differential\r\n\r\nDid your episodes of binge eating only occur when you refused to maintain an appropriate weight?
### Fear of Gaining Weight\r\n\r\nAt that time did you still feel fat or did you see yourself as too fat in some ways?
Were you still very much afraid that you could become fat, even after you'd lost a lot of weight?
### Distorted Body Image\r\n\r\nAt the time you were losing weight were you a lot more concerned about your weight and/or shape than most people your age?
Did you feel that parts of your body were still too fat when others thought that you were thin?
_INTERVIEWER: Is the participant female? _
### Amenorrhea\r\n\r\nHave you begun to have menstrual periods?
Do you have regular periods, meaning every month for at least six months?
If female & applicable: Did your periods ever stop?
How many months (maxium) did you miss in a row?
_INTERVIEWER: Did participant miss at least 3 cycles in a row?_
